  ('dietitian-moex-03293', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關glucose在人體之代謝的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["glucose在肝臟及肌肉中可合成為glycogen", "glucose在red blood cell中可經citric acid cycle代謝為CO 2", "glucose進入adipocyte需受insulin之促進", "glucose經glycolysis可代謝為pyruvate"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:31:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c4c4a20fa551", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e0664812025d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "106", "s": "0302", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-03294', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關胺基酸的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["豆類的限制胺基酸為離胺酸（lysine）", "穀類的限制胺基酸為離胺酸", "穀類與豆類混合的飲食可提供各類胺基酸", "芝麻、黃豆及小麥混合的飲食可提供各類胺基酸"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:31:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c4c4a20fa551", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e0664812025d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "106", "s": "0302", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-03295', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關飲食蛋白質消化吸收的敘述，何者正確？', '["必須將蛋白質完全分解為胺基酸才能被小腸絨毛吸收", "以被動擴散的方式與葡萄糖共同被吸收", "脂肪族胺基酸與芳香族胺基酸被吸收後由乳糜管回到肝臟", "所需之消化酵素來自胃、胰臟、小腸細胞"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:31:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c4c4a20fa551", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e0664812025d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "106", "s": "0302", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-03296', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關長期攝取高蛋白飲食（高於總熱量的35%）之敘述，何者錯誤？', '["必須攝取較多的維生素B、鋅、鐵等營養素", "可能會因此而攝取較多的飽和脂肪、膽固醇 6B", "動物性蛋白質中的胺基酸增加鈣自尿液流失", "葉酸、鎂、膳食纖維攝取量充足"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:31:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c4c4a20fa551", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e0664812025d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "106", "s": "0302", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-03297', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關服用單一胺基酸補充劑之敘述，何者正確？', '["會擾亂小腸胺基酸吸收的機制，造成胺基酸的不平衡", "如為必需胺基酸，會很快被人體吸收利用，併入體蛋白", "如為非必需胺基酸，氮會很快由腎臟排除，不會造成腎臟毒害", "運動員可因此而增加肌肉質量"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:31:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c4c4a20fa551", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e0664812025d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "106", "s": "0302", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-03298', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '早期因嬰兒奶粉配方組成不佳，僅含低量必需脂肪酸，餵食嬰兒後，造成皮膚乾燥脫屑，添加下列何種 脂肪酸後獲得改善？', '["亞麻油酸（linoleic acid）", "棕櫚酸（palmitic acid）", "硬脂酸（stearic acid）", "油酸（oleic acid）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:31:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c4c4a20fa551", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e0664812025d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "106", "s": "0302", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
